{"tid":1875361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【獨家消息！】本報獲悉至少2位滯留武漢港人已確診 求助港府但未有公開消息","createTime":"2020-02-11T17:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T18:31:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c916eb33f4bd3061015da47f5e1db68e03c2a56b","tid":1875361,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:51:18.000Z","msg":"【獨家消息！】政府日前公布有逾2000名香港人，因新型肺炎肆虐「封城」被困湖北省及武漢市，不過從未透露該批港人狀況及返港時間表。本報獲悉，至少2位當地港人已確診感染疫症，亦曾向港府求助，惟當局未有公開消息，政制及內地事務局至截稿前並無回覆。<br />\n<br />\n根據該封於周一(11日)撰寫、由政制及內地事務局向「武漢中心總醫院」寄出的特急信件中提到，至少2位滯留武漢港人，已同被確診感染新型肺炎，兩人姓李、屬父子關係，其中父親在較早前已入住該院，惟兒子在檢查確診後未獲安排入院。信中指政制及內地事務局收到兒子求助後，希望醫院通融接收患者，方便父子同住以保持聯繫及家人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n#信報 #武漢肺炎 #滯留武漢港人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongeconomicjournal/photos/a.553800847993875/3831150273592233/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongeconomicjournal%2Fphotos%2Fa.553800847993875%2F3831150273592233%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=14332a32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongeconomicjournal/photos/a.553800847993875/3831150273592233/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/84925723_3831150276925566_4375145599452839936_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_ohc=5Ul4qNnbi7MAX_b8gpm&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=7f63c32af903967054b9ecd47f2384ba&amp;oe=5EC2AA83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F84925723_3831150276925566_4375145599452839936_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_ohc%3D5Ul4qNnbi7MAX_b8gpm%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D7f63c32af903967054b9ecd47f2384ba%26oe%3D5EC2AA83&h=7d366aed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51492a766d49bf50fed51eddb806065dbfd1ca85","tid":1875361,"uid":49336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbBq46T.jpg\" da